---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';
---

<PageLayout
  title={`Privacy Policy — ${SITE.name}`}
  description={`How ${SITE.name} handles your data: all formatting runs in your browser, nothing is uploaded. Details on cookies, advertising and analytics.`}
  h1="Privacy Policy"
  updated="July 5, 2026"
  path="/privacy"
>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>{SITE.name}</strong> ("we", "us")
    handles information when you use our website and tools. Your privacy matters
    to us, and our tools are designed to keep your data on your own device.
  </p>

  <h2>Your content stays in your browser</h2>
  <p>
    All of our formatters — the AI Prompt Formatter, Markdown Formatter, and HTML
    Viewer — run entirely inside your web browser using client-side JavaScript.
    Any text you paste or type is processed locally on your device. We do
    <strong>not</strong> send, upload, store, or log the content you format.
  </p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <p>
    We do not require you to create an account or provide personal information to
    use our tools. Like most websites, our hosting provider and third-party
    services may automatically collect standard technical information such as:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your browser type and version, and device/operating system.</li>
    <li>Anonymized usage data such as pages visited and time on site.</li>
    <li>Your approximate location, derived from your IP address.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    This information is aggregated and used to understand traffic and improve the
    site. It does not include the content you format.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    We and our third-party partners may use cookies and similar technologies to
    operate the site, remember preferences, measure traffic, and serve
    advertising. You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings;
    disabling them will not affect the core functionality of our tools.
  </p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>
    We may display advertising provided by third-party ad networks, including
    Google AdSense, to keep our tools free.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on a
      user's prior visits to this and other websites.
    </li>
    <li>
      Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve
      ads to you based on your visits to this site and/or other sites on the
      internet.
    </li>
    <li>
      You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
      <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      For more options, visit
      <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">aboutads.info</a>.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    We may use privacy-respecting analytics tools to measure aggregate traffic.
    These tools do not have access to the content you format and are used only to
    understand how the site is used in aggregate.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party links</h2>
  <p>
    Our site may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for
    the privacy practices or content of those sites. We encourage you to review
    their privacy policies.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Our site is not directed to children under the age of 13, and we do not
    knowingly collect personal information from them.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    Depending on where you live (for example, under the GDPR or CCPA), you may
    have rights to access, correct, or delete personal information held about
    you. Because our tools do not collect your content, most requests relate only
    to standard analytics and advertising data handled by our third-party
    providers. Contact us if you have any questions.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be
    posted on this page with an updated revision date.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, email us at
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a> or use our
    <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
